Here's the updated version, separating what residents and officials can do:  

---

**Digital Barangay System**  

### **Residents Can:**  

#### **Create**  
<!-- - Log Complaints & Requests (e.g., barangay clearance, disputes)   -->
<!-- - Schedule Appointments (for permits, dispute resolution, assistance)   -->
<!-- - Register Businesses & Manage Permits   -->

#### **Read**  
- View Barangay Announcements  
- Check Online Directory (officials, services, emergency contacts)  
- Track Request/Complaint Status  

#### **Update**  
- Modify Appointments (reschedule/cancel visits)  
- Update Business Information  
- Edit Complaint/Request Details (before processing)  

#### **Delete**  
- Withdraw Complaints & Requests (before processing)  

---

### **Barangay Officials Can:**  

#### **Create**  
<!-- - Register Resident Accounts (full name, birthdate, address, contact) -->

#### **Read**  
<!-- - Access Resident Information for Verification & Assistance   -->

#### **Update**  
<!-- - Edit Resident Details (contact info, address updates)   -->
<!-- - Update Status of Requests/Complaints   -->
<!-- - Modify or Remove Business Registrations   -->
- Clear Notifications & Messages  

#### **Delete**  
<!-- - Remove Resident Accounts (upon request or official reasons)   -->
<!-- - Delete Entire Chat or Complaint History (if necessary)   -->